173 A.3d 602 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. HUMBERTO GONZALEZ, A/K/A SANTOS SOLARES, JOSE ROBE, SANTOS HOMBERTO M., SANTOS JOSE R., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-294 September Term 2017

079528 November 14, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002784-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
